10. Contact Us
If you would like to make use of any of the above rights or any other rights in relation to your personal data please click the "Data request" button on the top right corner of this privacy policy.

If you have any questions or comments about our privacy practices or this Privacy Statement please contact our Data Protection Officer at dpo@groupon.co.uk or privacy@groupon.co.uk You can also reach us via postal mail at the following address:

Groupon International Limited, ATTN: Data Protection Officer, Lower Ground Floor, Connaught House, 1 Burlington Road, Dublin 4, 216410 Ireland.

Our UK representative is MyCityDeal Limited (t/a Groupon UK), which has its address at 11-12 Aldgate Tower, 2 Leman Street, London E1 8FA.



11. Other Contacts
We are committed to working with you to obtain a fair resolution of any request, complaint, or concern about our use of your personal data. If, however, you believe that we have not been able to assist you, you have the right to make a complaint to the data protection authority in your country of residence, the ICO or to our Lead Supervisory Authority:

